metadata.name: face was reflected
metadata.description:
whose face IS more delicate than flowers, WHOSE black hair IS more PROFOUND THAN the night sky, AND whose TEMPERAMENT is more VIRTUOUS than a SCHOLAR?"



"Asked the girl, who was sitting before her dressing-table in the dark room, with her black hair tied in a thick braid at an Angle to her breast, in the light of the yellow candle, looking into the mirror before her.
